        </div>
        <div class="footer-col">
          <h4>Links</h4>
          <ul role="list">
            <li><a href="/career-odyssey" aria-label="Career Odyssey">Career Odyssey</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://curius.app/david-hoang" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="David Hoang on Curius (opens in new tab)">Curius</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.proofofconcept.pub" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Proof of Concept newsletter (opens in new tab)">Newsletter</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://blog.davidhoang.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="David Hoang's personal blog (opens in new tab)">Personal&nbsp;Blog</a></li>
            <li><a href="/rss.xml" type="application/rss+xml" aria-label="RSS feed for this website">RSS</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://substack.com/@davidhoang/notes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="David Hoang's Substack Notes (opens in new tab)">Substack Notes</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-col">
          <h4>Resources</h4>
          <ul role="list">
            <li><a href="/about" aria-label="About David Hoang">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/notes" aria-label="Digital garden notes">Notes</a></li>
            <li><a href="/now" aria-label="What David is doing now">Now</a></li>
